<a name="Creating_and_Editing_PDF_Forms">
</a>
<a aria-expanded="false" class="MCDropDownHotSpot dropDownHotspot MCDropDownHotSpot_" href="#">PDF -formatieren maken en werken</a>
</span>
<div class="MCDropDownBody dropDownBody">
<p>PDF-formulieren maken en bewerken wordt ondersteund in<span class="mc-variable MyVariables.Revu_eXtreme_--&gt;_Complete variable">Revu compleet</span>. Zie<a class="MCXref xref" href="Form-Menu.htm" xrefformat="{paratext}">Vormen</a>voor meer informatie.</p>
