<div class="MCDropDown MCDropDown_Closed dropDown">
<span class="MCDropDownHead dropDownHead">
<a aria-expanded="false" class="MCDropDownHotSpot dropDownHotspot MCDropDownHotSpot_ MCHotSpotImage" href="#">
<img alt="Closed" class="MCDropDown_Image_Icon" data-mc-alt2="Open" height="12" src="https://support.bluebeam.com/online-help/revu21/Skins/Default/Stylesheets/Images/transparent.gif" width="16"/>
